metadata.name: Candy Ransom
metadata.description:
Title: Candy Ransom  
Collection Size: 25  1/1 Picture Riddles  
Artist: Anthony Forchione  
License: Extended Editorial

Inspired by Walter Wick's work on the " I Spy" books I was fascinated with as a child, these sets were carefully constructed with real objects over days and sometimes weeks to make different themes and riddles for you to enjoy. 

These picture riddles will be released in sets of five, until a total collection size of twenty five is reached. 


Candy Ransom  
I Spy a strawberry, a cigar, baked beans from Boston,  
a necklace, a bunny, a roll of buttons,  
3 candy canes, 3 pixie sticks, a crown for Kings, 
And red wax lips
